	<text xml:lang="la">
		<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" subtype="metadata" n="1">Die Datierung ergibt sich aus der Bemerkung über <persName cert="high" ref="p8455">Hans Vogler</persName> (unten Z. 4-6); <persName ref="p1365" cert="high">Grynäus</persName> erwähnt dessen unehrenhafte Entlassung nach <placeName ref="l587" cert="high">Zürich</placeName> in seinem Brief vom Vortag (oben <ref target="file11547">Nr. 1504</ref>, 5f).</note>
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Commendo vobis hos fratres<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Unbekannt.</note> in domino.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Pietatem videntur intelligere.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Vestram ecclesiam cupiunt cognoscere, deinde in <placeName ref="l832">Galliam</placeName> redituri ea, ut videtur, lege, si inde ad nos transferre possint sua omnia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8455">Voglerum</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p8455">Hans Vogler d.J.</persName></note> coges, ut contiones sacras audiat quottidie, tum, ut eas alicui repetat.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Hęc verbi dei meditatio<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Vielleicht als</hi> meditacio <hi>zu lesen.</hi></note> faciet, arbitror, ut animus stabilimentum accipiat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale in domino, frater mihi dilectissime.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">24. aprilis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p1365">Simon Grynęus</persName> tuus.<pb type="edition" next="167"/></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la">Domino <persName ref="p495">Heinricho Bullingero</persName> suo, amico et fratri colendo.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l587">Tyguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
